Package it.polimi.ingsw.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Battlefield
    Battlefield Class represents the board where the game is played
    Cell
    Class Cell represents a single cell of the board
    GameState
    State of the game used for checking if requests are done right from the client
    Match
    Match class represents a match performed by a small group of players (2 or 3)
    Player
    Player class represents a player which takes part to the game
    Tower
    Tower class represents a tower object of the game
    Turn
    Turn class represents a generic turn that must be specialized with a card effect
    Worker
    Worker class represents a pawn of the game
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Block
    Represents the blocks used to build the towers in the game Each cell contains a tower, which starts from the GROUND level (basically it means that the tower has no levels)
    Color
    Represents the colors assigned to the players and their workers
    GameStep
    Game steps
